'''Kōshin-zuka Kofun''' (庚申塚古墳)
* {{ill|Kōshin-zuka Kofun (Takasaki)|ja|庚申塚古墳 (高崎市)|12=draft}} – A circular kofun located in [[Takasaki]], [[Gunma Prefecture]]. * {{ill|Kōshin-zuka Kofun (Saitama)|ja|庚申塚古墳 (さいたま市)|12=draft}} – A kofun located in [[Sakura-ku]], [[Saitama City]], [[Saitama Prefecture]]. * {{ill|Akiyama Kōshin-zuka Kofun|ja|秋山庚申塚古墳 (本庄市)|12=draft}} – A circular kofun in [[Honjō City]], Saitama Prefecture, part of the Akiyama Kofun Cluster. * {{ill|Kōshin-zuka Kofun (Tama)|ja|庚申塚古墳 (多摩市)|12=draft}} – A circular kofun in [[Tama City]], [[Tokyo]], part of the Wada Kofun Cluster. * {{ill|8=ja|9=庚申塚古墳_(飯綱町)|Kōshin-zuka Kofun (Iizuna)|12=draft}} – A keyhole-shaped kofun in [[Iizuna]], [[Nagano Prefecture]], known for yielding a lattice-patterned {{ill|hollow haniwa|ja|円筒埴輪|1=Cylindrical Haniwa|12=draft}}—the sixth such discovery nationwide. * {{ill|Kōshin-zuka Kofun (Fuji)|ja|庚申塚古墳 (富士市)|12=draft}} – A square-shaped kofun located in [[Fuji City]], [[Shizuoka Prefecture]]. * {{ill|Kōshin-zuka Kofun (Iwata)|ja|庚申塚古墳 (磐田市)|12=draft}} – A keyhole-shaped kofun located in [[Iwata City]], Shizuoka Prefecture. * {{ill|Jō Kōshin-zuka Kofun|ja|條庚申塚古墳 (御所市)|12=draft}} – A kofun located in [[Jō]], [[Gose City]], [[Nara Prefecture]].
{{aimai}}
{{citation needed|こうしんつかこふん}}
